(1, 1, 'Hello world!', 'hello-world', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/hello-world/', '2017-07-23 22:06:20', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!</p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2017-09-18 10:47:43'),
(2, 9, 'Best Institute of Entrepreneurship Development in India', 'best-institute-of-entrepreneurship-development-in-india', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/best-institute-of-entrepreneurship-development-in-india/', '2017-07-23 22:37:30', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>Introduction to entrepreneurshipFetched from a French word &#8220;entrepreneur&#8221; which means to take over something entrepreneurship links with innovation or introducing the world new and substantial thing, finance and business acumen can be considered in an effort to turn innovations into the economy. This may result in starting of a new <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/best-institute-of-entrepreneurship-development-in-india/" title="Best Institute of Entrepreneurship Development in India">[CONTINUE READING]</a></p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2017-09-18 10:47:43'),
(3, 10, 'Best Startup Accelerator in the East Chinaccelerator 2014 Year in Review', 'best-startup-accelerator-in-the-east-chinaccelerator-2014-year-in-review', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/best-startup-accelerator-in-the-east-chinaccelerator-2014-year-in-review/', '2017-07-23 22:38:49', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>Shanghai, China, December 26, 2014 &#8211; Chinaccelerator went through some huge changes this past year. At the end of 2013 it made the bold decision to move the operations to Shanghai, leaving behind its beautiful seaside office in Dalian where Chinaccelerator was born. The move was made easier through the <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/best-startup-accelerator-in-the-east-chinaccelerator-2014-year-in-review/" title="Best Startup Accelerator in the East Chinaccelerator 2014 Year in Review">[CONTINUE READING]</a></p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2017-09-18 10:47:43'),
(4, 11, 'What Qualities Ought To Be In A Reliable Rooster Incubator', 'what-qualities-ought-to-be-in-a-reliable-rooster-incubator', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/what-qualities-ought-to-be-in-a-reliable-rooster-incubator/', '2017-07-23 22:47:56', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>Like all man, a superb chicken incubator is tough to find. Rooster incubators are available in all shapes and sizes. Hen incubators share the wider enterprise ideals operated within business incubators and will normally assist their tenants with business planning, access to finance, mentoring, and different enterprise facilities. We supply <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/what-qualities-ought-to-be-in-a-reliable-rooster-incubator/" title="What Qualities Ought To Be In A Reliable Rooster Incubator">[CONTINUE READING]</a></p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2017-09-18 10:47:43'),
(5, 12, 'Entrepreneur Education', 'entrepreneur-education', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/entrepreneur-education/', '2017-07-23 22:53:06', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>Perfection is a strange phenomenon as it is to be achieved. To get perfected in any area one has to practice again and again and give is best to achieve this goal. The first step in this process is to get the related education; to go through the theory work <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/entrepreneur-education/" title="Entrepreneur Education">[CONTINUE READING]</a></p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2017-09-18 10:47:43'),
