(3666, 3805, 'As Google Maps Renames Neighborhoods, Residents Fume', 'as-google-maps-renames-neighborhoods-residents-fume', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/as-google-maps-renames-neighborhoods-residents-fume/', '2018-08-06 00:07:09', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>Google’s digital maps have become the world’s default atlas and the arbiter of what neighborhoods are called, even when many residents disagree.</p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2018-08-06 00:20:04'),
(3667, 3810, 'Top 5 Challenges Faced By The Australian Accounting Industry', 'top-5-challenges-faced-by-the-australian-accounting-industry', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/top-5-challenges-faced-by-the-australian-accounting-industry/', '2018-08-06 00:07:12', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>Accounting is a process through which the economic information of a company is identified, measured and communicated to the internal and external customers. It helps to identify the financial health of a company, which in turn facilitates to judge the performance of a company. So, it is very important to <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/top-5-challenges-faced-by-the-australian-accounting-industry/" title="Top 5 Challenges Faced By The Australian Accounting Industry">[CONTINUE READING]</a></p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2018-08-06 00:25:04'),
(3668, 3809, 'Best Big Cities for Starting a Business', 'best-big-cities-for-starting-a-business', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/best-big-cities-for-starting-a-business/', '2018-08-06 00:07:12', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>Low initial costs and modernized procedures make countries in Asia attractive to entrepreneurs. A couple of new business registrations occurred in East Asian and Pacific nations as recorded by the World Bank. The Organization for Economic Cooperation and Development reports that new enterprise creations have been positively developed internationally. Profit in <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/best-big-cities-for-starting-a-business/" title="Best Big Cities for Starting a Business">[CONTINUE READING]</a></p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2018-08-06 00:25:04'),
(3669, 3808, 'Don’t Let Expenses Be a Drag on Your Finances', 'dont-let-expenses-be-a-drag-on-your-finances', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/dont-let-expenses-be-a-drag-on-your-finances/', '2018-08-06 00:07:12', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>Summary: Lack of oversight, inefficient policy enforcement, not using data and analysis, and keeping processes manual are some reasons why expenses can be a drag on your organization&#8217;s finances. Employee-initiated expenses though are very necessary for the functioning of the firm, can be a huge drag on the company&#8217;s finances. <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/dont-let-expenses-be-a-drag-on-your-finances/" title="Don’t Let Expenses Be a Drag on Your Finances">[CONTINUE READING]</a></p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2018-08-06 00:25:04'),
(3670, 3813, 'Ooma Office Provides Enterprise Features at Small Business Prices', 'ooma-office-provides-enterprise-features-at-small-business-prices', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/ooma-office-provides-enterprise-features-at-small-business-prices/', '2018-08-07 00:07:10', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>Sponsored Post Ooma Office is a complete small business phone system that offers a virtual receptionist, conference call hosting, multi-device access, number porting, and much more; all at a price your small business can afford. Why You Still Need a Small Business Phone System Despite the rise of online search <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/ooma-office-provides-enterprise-features-at-small-business-prices/" title="Ooma Office Provides Enterprise Features at Small Business Prices">[CONTINUE READING]</a></p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2018-08-07 00:20:04'),
(3671, 3812, '10 Cybersecurity Myths Revealed! Is Your Small Business at Risk? (INFOGRAPHIC)', '10-cybersecurity-myths-revealed-is-your-small-business-at-risk-infographic', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/10-cybersecurity-myths-revealed-is-your-small-business-at-risk-infographic/', '2018-08-07 00:07:10', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>The dangers from cyber threats are very real, and the figures can be overwhelming to anyone reading the headlines. A new infographic by Varonis, titled &#8220;10 Cyber Security Myths Putting Your Business at Risk&#8221; identifies what is myth and what is reality. If you are like most small business owners, <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/10-cybersecurity-myths-revealed-is-your-small-business-at-risk-infographic/" title="10 Cybersecurity Myths Revealed! Is Your Small Business at Risk? (INFOGRAPHIC)">[CONTINUE READING]</a></p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2018-08-07 00:20:04'),
(3672, 3811, 'Want a Thriving Farm or Food Business? Food Safety Modernization Act Rules You MUST Know', 'want-a-thriving-farm-or-food-business-food-safety-modernization-act-rules-you-must-know', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/want-a-thriving-farm-or-food-business-food-safety-modernization-act-rules-you-must-know/', '2018-08-07 00:07:10', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>The Food Safety Modernization Act (FSMA) was originally signed into law back in 2011 to limit the risk of foodborne diseases. But this is the year that some of its rules go into effect for small farms and food handling facilities. Food Safety Modernization Act So in order to comply <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/want-a-thriving-farm-or-food-business-food-safety-modernization-act-rules-you-must-know/" title="Want a Thriving Farm or Food Business? Food Safety Modernization Act Rules You MUST Know">[CONTINUE READING]</a></p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2018-08-07 00:20:04'),
(3673, 3816, 'CRM Sales Are Through the Roof. So, Why Aren&#8217;t Your Sellers Using It? One Big Reason.', 'crm-sales-are-through-the-roof-so-why-arent-your-sellers-using-it-one-big-reason', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/crm-sales-are-through-the-roof-so-why-arent-your-sellers-using-it-one-big-reason/', '2018-08-07 00:07:11', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>The problem with CRM systems is that they aren&#8217;t built on methodology. They&#8217;re just a system of record.</p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2018-08-07 00:25:04'),
(3674, 3815, 'She Wants to Change the Face of the Industry', 'she-wants-to-change-the-face-of-the-industry', 'http://www.crowdbootstrap.net/she-wants-to-change-the-face-of-the-industry/', '2018-08-07 00:07:11', '<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>Despite the fact that African-American entrepreneurs are woefully under-represented in the cannabis industry, Marvina Thomas is turning the tide.</p>\n</div>', 'publish', 1, '2018-08-07 00:25:04'),
